data.description: GRAND 14' ceilings and a large open floor plan is what you will find when walking into this lovely home.  In addition, decorative and accent lighting illuminate the main areas of the home.  You will love to cook in this kitchen with stainless steel appliances, custom white tile backsplash, white Quartz countertops and modern gray cabinets accessorized with gold hardware.  There is an eat in breakfast bar as well as a formal dining breakfast area.  The primary suite has separate tub and shower with double vanities.  Conveniently located near Northwood High School, great shopping and dining.
